name: Moguls of the Flashmarble Graves
description: Part of the community of divers searching for the grave of Akak Gagak, the Moguls of the Flashmarble Graves are known for their exceptional frost flashmarble craftsmanship. Now finished uncovering the origin of the Clouddrop wisps, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
